    "en": {
      "title": "The interim budget is passed with a majority of 115 votes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The interim budget presented by the President for the next four months was passed with a majority of 115 votes.",
        "Samagi Jana Balawegaya and Pohottu Party's Dallas group and independent members including Wimal Weerawansa from the government abstained from voting.",
        "The National People's Party and the Tamil Organization voted against the budget."
      ],
